worked there at the church, he forced

00:12:59.100 --> 00:13:01.730
us to tithe. If you didn't tithe, they

00:13:01.740 --> 00:13:04.370
fired you. So I've been tithing ever

00:13:04.380 --> 00:13:06.769
since I started working at the church

00:13:06.779 --> 00:13:10.550
back in 2003. They forced us to tithe and

00:13:10.560 --> 00:13:11.930
they said, 'If you don't tithe, you're

00:13:11.930 --> 00:13:11.940
fired.'And

00:13:11.940 --> 00:13:14.449
so I was like, you know, that

00:13:14.459 --> 00:13:16.069
was a long time ago. I mean, that's going

00:13:16.079 --> 00:13:18.470
on over 20 some years now.

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:21.470
I've been tithing faithfully and giving

00:13:21.480 --> 00:13:24.650
my 10% and my offerings, believing God for

00:13:24.660 --> 00:13:26.690
increase. And so

00:13:26.700 --> 00:13:28.850
that's the way we did it. We believe

00:13:28.860 --> 00:13:31.370
by faith for everything we have, whether

00:13:31.380 --> 00:13:33.230
it's five dollars, ten dollars, whatever.

00:13:33.240 --> 00:13:35.509
You've got to believe God and start

00:13:35.519 --> 00:13:37.970
saying, 'Lord...'And you know, a lot of

00:13:37.980 --> 00:13:39.530
times you think, 'Well, how's it going to

00:13:39.540 --> 00:13:40.970
happen? How is God going to bring the

00:13:40.980 --> 00:13:43.670
increase in my house?'I don't

00:13:43.680 --> 00:13:46.550
limit myself to a job. I start, 'God, give

00:13:46.560 --> 00:13:48.410
me an idea.'Lord, I'm always thinking

00:13:48.420 --> 00:13:51.050
outside of the box. What can I do

00:13:51.060 --> 00:13:53.449
to work for myself to create wealth?

00:13:53.459 --> 00:13:55.490
That's when I started doing my dogs.

00:13:55.500 --> 00:13:57.230
I started having these little

00:13:57.240 --> 00:13:59.629
puppies, and the Lord gave us an idea to

00:13:59.639 --> 00:14:01.970
help with therapy dogs for people

00:14:01.980 --> 00:14:03.290
because my little girl is

00:14:03.300 --> 00:14:05.569
overcoming autism and she loves her

00:14:05.579 --> 00:14:07.610
little puppy, and my other little

00:14:07.620 --> 00:14:10.190
daughter loves her puppy. So we have

00:14:10.200 --> 00:14:12.769
these puppies and I sell therapy

00:14:12.779 --> 00:14:15.970
dogs to special needs kids and to

00:14:15.980 --> 00:14:18.889
elderly people who need a companion,

00:14:18.899 --> 00:14:21.230
so there's a lot of people that need

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:23.509
these dogs. So God gave me the idea for

00:14:23.519 --> 00:14:25.610
my family because I didn't have a lot of

00:14:25.620 --> 00:14:27.470
education.

00:14:27.480 --> 00:14:28.850
Of course, you all have heard my

00:14:28.860 --> 00:14:31.250
testimony about doing something other

00:14:31.260 --> 00:14:32.449
than cleaning, because I started doing

00:14:32.459 --> 00:14:34.370
the detailing business.

00:14:34.380 --> 00:14:36.170
I was like, 'Lord...'So the Lord gave me

00:14:36.180 --> 00:14:37.910
an idea, so I started cleaning cars

00:14:37.920 --> 00:14:39.889
because I used to clean cars for a major

00:14:39.899 --> 00:14:41.990
ministry. I started telling everybody

00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:44.090
I had an idea of doing mobile

00:14:44.100 --> 00:14:46.370
detailing, so I got me a mobile

00:14:46.380 --> 00:14:48.470
detailing trailer and I just go around

00:14:48.480 --> 00:14:51.170
cleaning cars for people. I'd be so

00:14:51.180 --> 00:14:52.370
excited because I could make a hundred

00:14:52.380 --> 00:14:54.949
dollars and clean a car. I detail, I wax

00:14:54.959 --> 00:14:57.290
it, do everything. I spent

00:14:57.300 --> 00:14:59.810
several hours doing it, but I got me a

00:14:59.820 --> 00:15:01.730
helper, and they helped me, and my brother.

00:15:01.740 --> 00:15:04.310
And so we cleaned the cars together and

00:15:04.320 --> 00:15:07.250
we would do things, wax the cars,

00:15:07.260 --> 00:15:09.590
and clean the carpets. I got me

00:15:09.600 --> 00:15:12.350
a carpet shampooer. I just started asking

00:15:12.360 --> 00:15:15.050
God for ways to create wealth so that I

00:15:15.060 --> 00:15:16.850
didn't have to work for seven dollars an

00:15:16.860 --> 00:15:18.710
hour because I didn't have an education.

00:15:18.720 --> 00:15:20.810
I was like, 'Man, I'm making minimum wage.

00:15:20.820 --> 00:15:23.329
You can't live on minimum

00:15:23.329 --> 00:15:23.339
wage.'And

00:15:23.339 --> 00:15:24.949
so I cleaned for the

00:15:24.959 --> 00:15:26.389
church, and they gave me a little raise,

00:15:26.399 --> 00:15:27.949
but I was still struggling. But I would

00:15:27.959 --> 00:15:30.590
work when I got off of work.

00:15:30.590 --> 00:15:30.600
After

00:15:30.600 --> 00:15:33.470
working my eight hours, I would

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:36.230
work another five hours at least cleaning

00:15:36.240 --> 00:15:38.509
cars, doing what I could to make money

00:15:38.519 --> 00:15:41.150
to be able to supply. And so God started

00:15:41.160 --> 00:15:43.250
increasing me and showing me, 'Hey, this is

00:15:43.260 --> 00:15:45.650
how you do business,'and having

00:15:45.660 --> 00:15:48.110
a business mindset as a Christian. Now,

00:15:48.120 --> 00:15:49.370
there's a lot of people in the

00:15:49.370 --> 00:15:49.380
comment

00:15:49.380 --> 00:15:50.689
section that don't believe that.

00:15:50.699 --> 00:15:52.550
Why do I need to be blessed? Because

00:15:52.560 --> 00:15:55.009
you're being selfish, bottom line. If you

00:15:55.019 --> 00:15:56.210
don't want to be blessed, you're being

00:15:56.220 --> 00:15:58.490
selfish, because the kingdom of God needs

00:15:58.500 --> 00:16:00.470
you, and you need to help them. This

00:16:00.480 --> 00:16:02.629
is how the church works. I worked for

00:16:02.639 --> 00:16:04.850
churches for years, and if the people

00:16:04.860 --> 00:16:06.769
didn't give, they were talking about how they

00:16:06.779 --> 00:16:08.269
couldn't pay the mortgage, they couldn't

00:16:08.279 --> 00:16:10.310
pay the electric bill, couldn't pay the

00:16:10.320 --> 00:16:12.650
water bill. You know, there's a lot

00:16:12.650 --> 00:16:12.660
of

00:16:12.660 --> 00:16:15.410
expense to a church. There's a lot to the

00:16:15.420 --> 00:16:17.990
expenses of a ministry, and people need

00:16:18.000 --> 00:16:20.150
to get it out of their head

00:16:20.160 --> 00:16:22.490
that it just happens. No, it doesn't just

00:16:22.500 --> 00:16:24.949
happen. It comes by people giving to the

00:16:24.959 --> 00:16:27.829
ministry. So,

00:16:27.839 --> 00:16:30.230
'Well, I just need to just take

00:16:30.240 --> 00:16:32.329
care of me.'Well, that's selfish.

00:16:32.339 --> 00:16:34.550
No, you need to believe God for more so

00:16:34.560 --> 00:16:36.590
you can help your neighbor. There is a

00:16:36.600 --> 00:16:38.150
storm coming. I'm going to tell you all,

00:16:38.160 --> 00:16:39.949
you all don't have a clue of how bad

00:16:39.959 --> 00:16:42.410
it's going to be. You don't. And I don't

00:16:42.420 --> 00:16:44.689
want to tell you in fear, but to tell you how

00:16:44.689 --> 00:16:44.699
bad—my

00:16:44.699 --> 00:16:46.910
dad and all of us have seen

00:16:46.920 --> 00:16:49.490
what's coming. It's bad, and I'm telling

00:16:49.500 --> 00:16:51.829
you the warnings from the Holy Ghost. If

00:16:51.839 --> 00:16:53.810
you jump in

00:16:53.810 --> 00:16:53.820
the

00:16:53.820 --> 00:16:56.030
river and you start falling, you're going

00:16:56.040 --> 00:16:57.410
to hear some things, and it's not about

00:16:57.420 --> 00:17:00.470
fear; it's about warning. Joseph was

00:17:00.480 --> 00:17:03.290
warned and he told Pharaoh, 'You need to

00:17:03.300 --> 00:17:06.169
store up seven years of food. You need to

00:17:06.179 --> 00:17:08.030
get ready for what's coming because there

00:17:08.030 --> 00:17:08.040
are

00:17:08.040 --> 00:17:10.010
seven years of plenty and

00:17:10.020 --> 00:17:12.470
seven years of famine.'I'm telling you

00:17:12.480 --> 00:17:14.689
all, there's a shaking coming to this

00:17:14.699 --> 00:17:17.449
nation. We have been spoiled, and you

00:17:17.459 --> 00:17:18.350
know, when a lot of people say, 'Well,

00:17:18.360 --> 00:17:20.270
that's not going to happen to

00:17:20.270 --> 00:17:20.280
us,'listen,

00:17:20.280 --> 00:17:23.630
it happened not even a

00:17:23.640 --> 00:17:26.630
hundred years ago. My granny tells me all

00:17:26.640 --> 00:17:29.330
kinds of stories; she was 106 years

00:17:29.340 --> 00:17:31.250
old. She talked about just saving foil. She

00:17:31.260 --> 00:17:32.930
wouldn't even throw foil away.

00:17:32.940 --> 00:17:36.110
She was so scared to throw foil away,

00:17:36.120 --> 00:17:37.430
thinking that there was another

00:17:37.440 --> 00:17:39.529
depression coming in her lifetime. She

00:17:39.539 --> 00:17:41.870
didn't even trust banks. She was scared

00:17:41.880 --> 00:17:43.430
spitless to even put her money in the

00:17:43.440 --> 00:17:45.110
bank. She would hide it all over

00:17:45.120 --> 00:17:47.270
the place. Before she

00:17:47.280 --> 00:17:49.190
went home to the Lord, she'd dig a hole

00:17:49.200 --> 00:17:50.690
in the yard, put it in a little

00:17:50.700 --> 00:17:52.909
canister, and

00:17:52.919 --> 00:17:54.529
shove it down in the yard, bury it. You

00:17:54.539 --> 00:17:55.789
didn't even know.

00:17:55.799 --> 00:17:57.529
I mean, that's the kind of stuff they

00:17:57.539 --> 00:17:59.870
lived through, and that was a terrible time

00:17:59.880 --> 00:18:01.850
in the 1930s, I believe is when it was.

00:18:01.860 --> 00:18:04.130
That wasn't that long ago. But we

00:18:04.140 --> 00:18:06.529
have such an entitlement right now as a

00:18:06.539 --> 00:18:07.789
culture

00:18:07.799 --> 00:18:10.190
because we've had everything—we've had

00:18:10.200 --> 00:18:11.630
air conditioning, we've had all the stuff.

00:18:11.640 --> 00:18:13.250
They didn't have it, granny, they didn't

00:18:13.260 --> 00:18:15.590
have anything. They were dead broke. They

00:18:15.600 --> 00:18:18.710
had to use the flour sacks from the

00:18:18.710 --> 00:18:18.720
flour

00:18:18.720 --> 00:18:20.810
to make clothes out of

00:18:20.820 --> 00:18:22.370
it so that they would have clothes to

00:18:22.380 --> 00:18:25.010
wear to go to school. Granny didn't have

00:18:25.010 --> 00:18:25.020
anything.

00:18:25.020 --> 00:18:27.770
They lived off of

00:18:27.780 --> 00:18:30.890
beans and rice and possum

00:18:30.900 --> 00:18:34.310
out of the yard—nasty stuff. Even

00:18:34.320 --> 00:18:36.169
before she went home to be with the Lord,

00:18:36.179 --> 00:18:38.630
she would go outside and be digging in a

00:18:38.640 --> 00:18:40.490
ditch and pull up some weeds and cut the

00:18:40.500 --> 00:18:42.529
roots off and go in and boil it and eat

00:18:42.539 --> 00:18:43.310
it.

00:18:43.320 --> 00:18:45.470
But she lived to 106 years old; she could

00:18:45.480 --> 00:18:46.970
live off anything. She'd go, 'Those are

00:18:46.980 --> 00:18:49.070
poke greens; those are

00:18:49.080 --> 00:18:51.049
dandelion greens.'She would

00:18:51.059 --> 00:18:52.970
go out there and just start digging in

00:18:52.980 --> 00:18:54.409
the yard because they lived off of that

00:18:54.409 --> 00:18:54.419
for

00:18:54.419 --> 00:18:56.450
years. That's how they lived. They

00:18:56.460 --> 00:18:58.730
starved almost a lot of times, and the

00:18:58.740 --> 00:19:00.409
farmers would all go together. She would

00:19:00.419 --> 00:19:01.730
tell me about it; they would

00:19:01.740 --> 00:19:03.470
get the eggs from the farmers and they

00:19:03.480 --> 00:19:05.390
would trade, they would barter, and

00:19:05.400 --> 00:19:07.130
they did all kinds of stuff just to

00:19:07.140 --> 00:19:11.390
survive. Even to take a bath,

00:19:11.400 --> 00:19:13.430
before she went home,

00:19:13.440 --> 00:19:16.250
she wouldn't even turn on the shower;

00:19:16.260 --> 00:19:18.049
she would just sponge bath

00:19:18.059 --> 00:19:20.390
herself every single day when she

00:19:20.400 --> 00:19:21.830
would be outside working. She had a

00:19:21.840 --> 00:19:23.930
sponge bath, and then one time a week

00:19:23.940 --> 00:19:26.029
she took a bath. That's what she did. And

00:19:26.039 --> 00:19:27.590
that was just up

00:19:27.600 --> 00:19:30.409
until a couple of years ago when she went home.

00:19:30.419 --> 00:19:33.230
That's the way she lived; it affected her

00:19:33.240 --> 00:19:36.049
that much. And so I'm trying to tell you

00:19:36.059 --> 00:19:38.750
all something. I don't know how

00:19:38.760 --> 00:19:40.549
many of you all have had relatives that

00:19:40.559 --> 00:19:42.650
had hard times and lived in hard times

00:19:42.660 --> 00:19:46.130
and saw that during the Depression. I

00:19:46.140 --> 00:19:48.529
pray we never see this stuff, I really do.

00:19:48.539 --> 00:19:50.870
I intercede all the time. But I'm telling

00:19:50.880 --> 00:19:54.169
you, I've seen pictures and the Lord will

00:19:54.179 --> 00:19:57.770
give me warnings about the wars and

00:19:57.780 --> 00:19:58.450
about

00:19:58.460 --> 00:20:00.890
people living in poverty and things

00:20:00.900 --> 00:20:03.770
happening. And God wants to

00:20:03.780 --> 00:20:05.350
raise up

00:20:05.360 --> 00:20:07.730
multi-millionaires for these last days

00:20:07.740 --> 00:20:11.750
so that we will preach the gospel

00:20:11.760 --> 00:20:13.850
and have money to help support these

00:20:13.860 --> 00:20:17.210
preachers, help tent revivals, churches,

00:20:17.210 --> 00:20:17.220
and

00:20:17.220 --> 00:20:19.430
things like that, so that they won't all

00:20:19.440 --> 00:20:21.890
go under. There are some churches, like the

00:20:21.900 --> 00:20:24.770
last church I worked

00:20:24.770 --> 00:20:24.780
for, where

00:20:24.780 --> 00:20:26.570
they borrowed seven

00:20:26.580 --> 00:20:29.510
million dollars for the mortgage on

00:20:29.510 --> 00:20:29.520
the building. A monthly

00:20:29.520 --> 00:20:31.370
payment on seven percent

00:20:31.380 --> 00:20:32.690
interest

00:20:32.700 --> 00:20:36.470
over 30 years—that's a big note.

00:20:36.480 --> 00:20:38.450
Seriously, that comes every month.

00:20:38.460 --> 00:20:40.130
There's a lot of churches in America;

00:20:40.130 --> 00:20:40.140
you've

00:20:40.140 --> 00:20:42.110
got to think of all these

00:20:42.110 --> 00:20:42.120
megachurches

00:20:42.120 --> 00:20:43.490
around here in these

00:20:43.500 --> 00:20:44.750
big towns that have all these fancy

00:20:44.760 --> 00:20:45.650
buildings that

00:20:45.650 --> 00:20:45.660
are

00:20:45.660 --> 00:20:47.930
not paid for.

00:20:47.940 --> 00:20:50.330
I believe

00:20:50.340 --> 00:20:52.250
a lot of them will probably close their

00:20:52.260 --> 00:20:54.289
doors because they won't be able to afford them.

00:20:54.289 --> 00:20:54.299
There will

00:20:54.299 --> 00:20:55.610
be a lot of home churches,

00:20:55.620 --> 00:20:57.110
Bible studies, and

00:20:57.110 --> 00:20:57.120
smaller gatherings.

00:20:57.120 --> 00:20:58.789
I've seen

00:20:58.789 --> 00:20:58.799
these

00:20:58.799 --> 00:21:01.549
smaller

00:21:01.559 --> 00:21:03.049
gatherings, and whenever

00:21:03.059 --> 00:21:05.450
major events take place, there will be big

00:21:05.460 --> 00:21:07.610
gatherings with big tents,

00:21:07.620 --> 00:21:09.650
tent revivals, and

00:21:09.660 --> 00:21:11.450
healing revivals. It's going to

00:21:11.460 --> 00:21:14.270
happen like the old 1950s tent

00:21:14.270 --> 00:21:14.280
revivals

00:21:14.280 --> 00:21:17.090
with A.A. Allen, Jack

00:21:17.090 --> 00:21:17.100
Coe,

00:21:17.100 --> 00:21:19.070
Oral Roberts, Kathryn

00:21:19.070 --> 00:21:19.080
Kuhlman,

00:21:19.080 --> 00:21:20.750
and all of them. It's going to be

00:21:20.760 --> 00:21:25.010
major tent revivals again. R.W.

00:21:25.010 --> 00:21:25.020
Schambach,

00:21:25.020 --> 00:21:27.289
we're going to see this again.

00:21:27.299 --> 00:21:30.470
I hope you all understand that I

00:21:30.480 --> 00:21:32.390
never want to preach fear, but you

00:21:32.390 --> 00:21:32.400
have

00:21:32.400 --> 00:21:35.090
to understand that you

00:21:35.090 --> 00:21:35.100
must

00:21:35.100 --> 00:21:37.450
sow a seed to reap a harvest.

00:21:37.460 --> 00:21:40.510
Every seed produces after its own kind;

00:21:40.520 --> 00:21:43.370
finances happen the same way. You

00:21:43.370 --> 00:21:43.380
might say

00:21:43.380 --> 00:21:45.830
you don't give to

00:21:45.840 --> 00:21:49.789
get, but a farmer plants a seed of corn

00:21:49.799 --> 00:21:53.570
in the field to reap corn. He plants

00:21:53.580 --> 00:21:57.289
peas in the field to reap peas. You

00:21:57.299 --> 00:22:00.230
sow in the kingdom of God to reap so you

00:22:00.240 --> 00:22:03.890
can take care of yourself too. I give so

00:22:03.900 --> 00:22:06.169
that I can sow to get what God has

00:22:06.179 --> 00:22:08.810
promised me in His word: 'good measure,

00:22:08.810 --> 00:22:08.820
pressed

00:22:08.820 --> 00:22:11.690
down, shaken together, and running

00:22:11.700 --> 00:22:14.029
over will men give unto you.'God will

00:22:14.039 --> 00:22:16.909
give you ideas to get wealth so that you

00:22:16.919 --> 00:22:19.250
don't have to struggle. Maybe

00:22:19.250 --> 00:22:19.260
you're

00:22:19.260 --> 00:22:22.130
good at making

00:22:24.000 --> 00:22:26.870
pies; start selling them at a bakery

00:22:26.880 --> 00:22:30.230
or something there or online.

00:22:35.159 --> 00:22:38.630
Whatever you put your hands to will

00:22:38.640 --> 00:22:41.029
prosper; He told us this in Deuteronomy

00:22:41.039 --> 00:22:44.630
28. Read

00:22:44.640 --> 00:22:46.669
that over and over again about

00:22:46.679 --> 00:22:48.710
the blessings—everything you put your

00:22:48.720 --> 00:22:51.049
hands to will prosper. I meditate on it and get it down inside

00:22:51.049 --> 00:22:51.059
of me. The more you

00:22:51.059 --> 00:22:53.450
meditate on

00:22:53.460 --> 00:22:55.850
the word,

00:22:55.860 --> 00:22:58.130
the more it

00:22:58.140 --> 00:23:00.590
will become

00:23:00.600 --> 00:23:03.110
alive inside your spirit: you are

00:23:03.120 --> 00:23:05.390
the head and not the tail, you're above

00:23:05.400 --> 00:23:07.370
and not beneath, and you'll go through and

00:23:07.380 --> 00:23:09.890
not go under.

00:23:09.900 --> 00:23:11.750
You just have to get that word inside

00:23:11.750 --> 00:23:11.760
you;

00:23:11.760 --> 00:23:13.970
everything you put your hands to will

00:23:13.980 --> 00:23:16.310
prosper. Quote those

00:23:16.320 --> 00:23:18.590
scriptures and believe them for

00:23:18.600 --> 00:23:21.590
what's coming. I'm telling you all, a

00:23:21.600 --> 00:23:23.630
storm is coming. A lot of you don't

00:23:23.640 --> 00:23:25.430
want to hear that, thinking the Rapture of

00:23:25.440 --> 00:23:27.350
the church is coming before that happens,

00:23:27.350 --> 00:23:27.360
but

00:23:27.360 --> 00:23:30.590
no, you're wrong. Perilous times are

00:23:30.600 --> 00:23:33.110
coming. I hope you

00:23:33.120 --> 00:23:35.390
understand that before the birthing

00:23:35.390 --> 00:23:35.400
pains—it

00:23:35.400 --> 00:23:39.470
says as labor pains come upon a

00:23:39.480 --> 00:23:43.130
woman, so will it be. Jesus

00:23:43.140 --> 00:23:44.990
warned us about the birthing pains.

00:23:44.990 --> 00:23:45.000
They

00:23:45.000 --> 00:23:48.070
start out small

00:23:48.080 --> 00:23:51.830
and

00:23:53.340 --> 00:23:55.850
get more and

00:23:55.860 --> 00:23:58.130
more until

00:23:58.140 --> 00:24:00.409
the birth of the baby. Every woman who has

00:24:00.409 --> 00:24:00.419
a child

00:24:00.419 --> 00:24:03.110
knows this; it does not

00:24:03.120 --> 00:24:07.370
slack off, it increases

00:24:07.370 --> 00:24:07.380
until

00:24:07.380 --> 00:24:09.529
it's unbearable.

00:24:11.640 --> 00:24:14.029
That's the way it's going to be:

00:24:14.039 --> 00:24:16.130
more frequent

00:24:18.230 --> 00:24:18.240
until

00:24:19.799 --> 00:24:22.010
the birthing of us leaving in the

00:24:22.020 --> 00:24:23.450
Rapture of the church. Some of you

00:24:23.460 --> 00:24:24.890
don't believe in the Rapture;

00:24:24.900 --> 00:24:28.190
that's fine, I do,

00:24:28.200 --> 00:24:31.430
but we are going to see some things. The

00:24:31.440 --> 00:24:32.990
weather's going to start getting

00:24:33.000 --> 00:24:34.610
even crazier:

00:24:34.620 --> 00:24:38.990
the heatwaves, the rain, and the droughts.

00:24:39.000 --> 00:24:41.930
I really believe with

00:24:41.940 --> 00:24:43.130
all my heart we're going to see it.

00:24:43.140 --> 00:24:44.390
That's why the Lord has talked to me

00:24:44.400 --> 00:24:46.789
about having a well,

00:24:46.799 --> 00:24:48.770
water shortages,

00:24:50.700 --> 00:24:53.149
a generator for power,

00:24:53.159 --> 00:24:55.370
and

00:24:55.380 --> 00:24:57.590
food storage. He talked to me about

00:24:57.600 --> 00:25:00.529
securing your home better.

00:25:00.539 --> 00:25:02.630
Just

00:25:02.640 --> 00:25:04.549
three years ago, people

00:25:04.559 --> 00:25:06.590
were going crazy in San Francisco,

00:25:06.590 --> 00:25:06.600
robbing

00:25:06.600 --> 00:25:09.010
and looting

00:25:09.020 --> 00:25:11.930
whenever COVID was going on. People

00:25:11.940 --> 00:25:13.789
were

00:25:13.799 --> 00:25:16.490
fighting over toilet paper; you

00:25:16.490 --> 00:25:16.500
would

00:25:16.500 --> 00:25:18.289
almost lose your life over a roll of

00:25:18.299 --> 00:25:21.230
toilet paper. If there's no food

00:25:21.240 --> 00:25:22.789
on the shelf—and I warned you there

00:25:22.789 --> 00:25:22.799
were

00:25:22.799 --> 00:25:24.409
cobwebs in

00:25:24.419 --> 00:25:27.169
some supermarkets—it's even

00:25:27.169 --> 00:25:27.179
worse in

00:25:27.179 --> 00:25:29.750
major

00:25:29.760 --> 00:25:34.370
populated areas.

00:25:34.380 --> 00:25:36.830
If they're willing to hurt you for a

00:25:36.840 --> 00:25:38.690
roll of toilet paper, how much more are

00:25:38.700 --> 00:25:40.010
they going to hurt you for a gallon of

00:25:40.020 --> 00:25:42.230
milk,

00:25:42.240 --> 00:25:44.930
bread,

00:25:44.940 --> 00:25:48.470
canned food, or meat?

00:25:48.480 --> 00:25:51.409
Spam is going to become

00:25:51.419 --> 00:25:53.810
a big deal.

00:25:55.919 --> 00:25:58.610
People get crazy

00:25:58.620 --> 00:26:01.190
when they can't get food.

00:26:06.299 --> 00:26:08.630
I'm just

00:26:08.640 --> 00:26:10.850
trying to help you; I can only lead you

00:26:10.860 --> 00:26:12.350
to the water, but I can't force you to

00:26:12.360 --> 00:26:14.269
drink. I'm believing God for the Iraqi

00:26:14.279 --> 00:26:16.850
dinar.

00:26:16.860 --> 00:26:19.010
The Lord showed me

00:26:19.020 --> 00:26:21.769
Babylon rising again.

00:26:21.779 --> 00:26:25.610
Babylon was the

00:26:25.620 --> 00:26:28.610
breadbasket of the world at one time,

00:26:28.620 --> 00:26:30.649
and I believe it will be

00:26:30.659 --> 00:26:33.110
again. I

00:26:33.120 --> 00:26:34.850
believe there's a shifting coming in

00:26:34.860 --> 00:26:37.190
Iraq.

00:26:39.299 --> 00:26:42.769
I

00:26:42.779 --> 00:26:45.169
believe the people who are listening to

00:26:45.179 --> 00:26:47.570
the Spirit of God about crypto and

00:26:47.580 --> 00:26:49.850
these things are not

00:26:49.860 --> 00:26:51.769
going to struggle.

00:26:51.779 --> 00:26:55.490
God's going to give creative ideas

00:26:55.500 --> 00:26:57.649
to provide for the

00:26:57.659 --> 00:26:59.470
people who are listening to Him

00:26:59.470 --> 00:26:59.480
and

00:26:59.480 --> 00:27:02.570
praying

00:27:02.580 --> 00:27:06.289
in

00:27:06.299 --> 00:27:08.390
the Spirit. You need to read your Bible

00:27:08.400 --> 00:27:10.730
and pray in tongues.

00:27:20.220 --> 00:27:23.210
The Lord wants everybody to

00:27:25.260 --> 00:27:27.169
have that

00:27:27.179 --> 00:27:29.390
prayer

00:27:29.400 --> 00:27:31.730
language so you don't have to let the

00:27:31.740 --> 00:27:34.430
devil hear you.

00:27:34.440 --> 00:27:37.190
Walking in

00:27:37.200 --> 00:27:39.049
the Holy Ghost is what you're going to

00:27:39.059 --> 00:27:42.289
have to do in these last

00:27:42.289 --> 00:27:42.299
days—knowing

00:27:42.299 --> 00:27:44.810
the name of Jesus and understanding

00:27:44.810 --> 00:27:44.820
the

00:27:44.820 --> 00:27:48.470
power

00:27:48.470 --> 00:27:48.480
in

00:27:48.480 --> 00:27:51.250
the blood.

00:27:58.440 --> 00:28:01.430
Just

00:28:01.440 --> 00:28:03.289
like the greats

00:28:03.289 --> 00:28:03.299
like

00:28:03.299 --> 00:28:04.669
Smith Wigglesworth,

00:28:04.679 --> 00:28:07.250
walking in the authority of the believer.

00:28:07.260 --> 00:28:09.409
I hope I didn't freak you out; I'm just

00:28:09.419 --> 00:28:11.090
trying to be real with you

00:28:11.100 --> 00:28:13.250
today. It's not really a sermon; it's just

00:28:13.260 --> 00:28:15.409
me being real and

00:28:15.409 --> 00:28:15.419
telling

00:28:15.419 --> 00:28:17.990
you where I'm at. I don't

00:28:18.000 --> 00:28:20.930
live in fear, but

00:28:20.940 --> 00:28:23.810
I live with my ear towards Him.

00:28:23.820 --> 00:28:26.090
Regarding

00:28:26.100 --> 00:28:28.070
the financial

00:28:28.080 --> 00:28:29.570
outpouring,

00:28:29.580 --> 00:28:31.549
not everybody's going to participate;

00:28:34.320 --> 00:28:35.810
some people will stay broke, just like it was

00:28:35.820 --> 00:28:37.990
in the.com

00:28:38.000 --> 00:28:40.430
era.

00:28:40.440 --> 00:28:43.070
Jesus told us the

00:28:43.070 --> 00:28:43.080
poor

00:28:43.080 --> 00:28:45.470
will be with you always.

00:28:50.640 --> 00:28:52.310
I don't want to be one

00:28:52.320 --> 00:28:53.870
of them; I want to be

00:28:53.880 --> 00:28:55.310
the man with the pitcher in his

00:28:55.320 --> 00:28:57.649
hand helping folks,

00:28:57.649 --> 00:28:57.659
being

00:28:57.659 --> 00:28:59.570
able to say

00:28:59.580 --> 00:29:02.149
I can help you with some rice or

00:29:03.840 --> 00:29:06.590
beans. But

00:29:07.980 --> 00:29:09.830
it takes money to get a surplus;

00:29:09.840 --> 00:29:12.590
groceries are expensive right now. To go

00:29:12.600 --> 00:29:15.470
to Sam's or Costco and buy in bulk

00:29:15.480 --> 00:29:17.450
takes thousands of

00:29:17.460 --> 00:29:19.610
dollars.

00:29:28.559 --> 00:29:31.310
God

00:29:31.320 --> 00:29:33.710
takes care of the widow, the orphan, and the sparrow;

00:29:35.460 --> 00:29:37.850
how much more does He care about

00:29:37.860 --> 00:29:38.930
you?

00:29:47.039 --> 00:29:49.010
Start studying people

00:29:49.010 --> 00:29:49.020
like

00:29:49.020 --> 00:29:51.409
George

00:29:51.419 --> 00:29:53.690
Mueller and how he took care of the

00:29:53.700 --> 00:29:56.570
orphans.

00:30:05.399 --> 00:30:08.210
I watched it on

00:30:08.210 --> 00:30:08.220
VeggieTales,

00:30:08.220 --> 00:30:09.889
but then I

00:30:09.889 --> 00:30:09.899
studied and realized

00:30:09.899 --> 00:30:11.750
this

00:30:11.760 --> 00:30:13.730
man really existed

00:30:13.730 --> 00:30:13.740
and

00:30:13.740 --> 00:30:15.649
lived by faith. You're going

00:30:15.649 --> 00:30:15.659
to have to learn to

00:30:15.659 --> 00:30:18.590
live by faith.

00:30:22.440 --> 00:30:24.470
I hope

00:30:24.480 --> 00:30:26.269
this

00:30:26.279 --> 00:30:28.789
talk blessed you today.

00:30:28.799 --> 00:30:31.370
Thank you for watching,

00:30:31.380 --> 00:30:33.710
the subscribes,

00:30:33.720 --> 00:30:35.750
the likes, and

00:30:35.750 --> 00:30:35.760
the

00:30:35.760 --> 00:30:38.389
Facebook shares.

00:30:38.399 --> 00:30:42.590
Do not share my videos on YouTube. I

00:30:42.600 --> 00:30:44.570
mean that when I'm telling

00:30:44.580 --> 00:30:46.250
you to share my video, do not share my

00:30:46.260 --> 00:30:48.289
videos on YouTube. You're not copying my

00:30:48.299 --> 00:30:50.330
material and putting it on your

00:30:50.340 --> 00:30:53.110
page; this is my stuff.

00:30:53.120 --> 00:30:55.610
Preach your own sermon and put your own

00:30:55.620 --> 00:30:57.590
thing out there. Don't put my stuff

00:30:57.600 --> 00:30:59.810
out there on your YouTube channel or

00:30:59.820 --> 00:31:02.029
whatever. You can share it on

00:31:02.039 --> 00:31:03.350
your Facebook; that's what I mean when

00:31:03.360 --> 00:31:05.149
I'm saying to share it. Share it on

00:31:05.159 --> 00:31:07.789
Facebook, Instagram, or

00:31:07.799 --> 00:31:11.210
Twitter. All right, well we thank

00:31:11.220 --> 00:31:13.250
you so much for your support. Put a

00:31:13.260 --> 00:31:14.870
smile on your face and a song in your

00:31:14.880 --> 00:31:16.970
heart. We love you so much and we'll see

00:31:16.980 --> 00:31:19.880
you next time. Bye-bye.

